name: Developing Event Timeline
description: Creating a step-by-step timeline to keep your event planning organized and on track.

nodes.name: llm
nodes.title: Answers
nodes.description: Answer a question using a large language model. Chat history can be used to maintain context between messages.

input_config.human_message: Develop a timeline for the [event name] {{event_name}}, style of the event {{type}}, from [start date] last in {{estimalted_duration}} . Include and {{key_stages}} of milestones and each milestone's details.

date.title: Event Date
date.description: The date your event will take place.

type.title: Event Type (Optional)
type.description: Select the event type (e.g., conference, workshop, webinar) to pre-populate common tasks based on that format.

key_stages.title: Major Event Stages (Optional)
key_stages.description: List the key stages of your event (e.g., pre-event planning, event setup, event execution, post-event follow-up).

estimalted_duration.title: Estimated Duration (Optional)
estimalted_duration.description: Provide an estimated length of the event (e.g., one day, multi-day) to help gauge the timeline scope.
